						Denis Pryanichnikov
					</div>

					<div class="our-people-item__position">
						Head of Kazakhstan Office
					</div>

					<div class="our-people-item__descr">
						Denis has over 20 years of experience in financial sector joining us from Moscow Exchange where he was a Head of Innovation and investment market focusing on primary market services for growth companies and SMEs. Prior to that he was a Head of investment products at IFD Kapital, senior analyst at Alfa bank, Head of research and IB specialist at Otkritie. <br><br>
						At ITI Capital, Denis is in charge for the development of international presence in Kazakhstan and Qatar with the focus on capital markets and transactions and advisory.
					</div>
				</div>

