					<div class="our-people-item__name">
						Gene Moldavsky
					</div>

					<div class="our-people-item__position">
						CEO ITI Digital
					</div>

					<div class="our-people-item__descr">
						Gene is an Accenture and PwC trained IT/strategic consultant turned TMT investment banker at Renaissance Capital, UBS and Alfa Bank.  After stepping down as Head of IB at Alfa Bank, Gene founded several start-ups in the digital health and AgTech space before catching the crypto bug in 2017, which lead to the creation of ITI Digital.  Gene graduated Magna Cum Laude from Boston University and London School of Economics (LSE) with double degrees in Finance and MIS, and recently completed the Oxford Blockchain Program.
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="our-people-item">
					<div class="our-people-item__img">
						<img src="./img/yakovlev.jpg" alt="">
					</div>

					<div class="our-people-item__name">
						Gleb Yakovlev
					</div>

					<div class="our-people-item__position">
						Managing Director of ITI Funds
					</div>

